original_title: 戦慄怪奇ファイル 超コワすぎ！ FILE-02 暗黒奇譚！蛇女の怪
overview: Kudo receives a video shot by a job-hopper named Sakurai. The video shows a beautiful woman who visits the side of a river in the countryside. Sakurai has fallen in love with her and visits her home, but it's there he witnesses a terrifying scene.
title: Senritsu Kaiki File Super Kowa Too! Dark Mystery: Snake Woman
